data.description: Motivated Seller!!!PRICE REDUCTION!!!Gorgeous single family home in the Williamsbridge section of the Bronx. This home comes with 3 bedrooms, 1.5 bathrooms, hardwood floors, additional rooms in the basement for entertainment and storage. Conveniently located minutes from public transportation and walking distance from White Plains Rd. Lastly, there is ample private space in front of the home to put patio furniture. Plus private parking behind the home.
